.Pa auth .
.El
.Sh LEVELS
.Bl -tag -width 11n -compact
.It emerg
.It alert
.It crit
.It err
.It warning
.It notice
.It info
.It debug
.It panic
deprecated synonym for
.Pa emerg .
.It error
deprecated synonym for
.Ar err .
.It warn
deprecated synonym for
.Pa warning .
.El
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width indent
.It /etc/vlogger
An optional executable file that is used to to handle the messages.
It is executed with
.Ar tag ,
.Ar level
and
.Ar facility
as arguments
and replaces the
.Nm
process.
.El
.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Ex -std
.Sh EXAMPLES
.Pa /etc/vlogger :
.Bd -literal -offset indent
#!/bin/sh
exec svlogd /var/log/$1
.Ed
